message.body: i'm having a bday bbq a week from sunday at liberty lands. starting at 4. hilary will be there. hope you can come-
I saw it on facebook! I think I can come, is it a potluck?
i think so. i'm not sure how to plan for it foodwise. lots of vegetarians will be coming.
I'm good. Stressing over a paper I'm having a hard time writing. How are u?
so so. i hit a biker with my car and feel terrible about it. it was neither of our faults. she went to the hospital.
Oh no! Were you hurt at all? I'm sorry, that's very scary.
no. she broke my tail light and hit her head on my trunk.
Oh man, that's rough. Don't feel bad tho, it happens. It feels worse when you cycle a lot I think.
i'm going to see my old therapist about it today.
That's a good idea. It might be nice to see her
yeah. she just seemed really messed up - like prob a concussion.
